sentences: He released 24 albums and mixtapes since his debut in 2008.
Ras G started his career in 2005.
He released Brotha from Anotha Planet in 2009.
His solo album, Down 2 Earth, was released on Ramp Recordings in 2011.
He released a free EP, titled Ainat, in 2012.
In 2013, he released Back on the Planet on Brainfeeder.
He died in the Leimert Park neighborhood of Los Angeles on July 29, 2019, aged 40.
